{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 5,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 289.869,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.065,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after we had come down",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.245,
      "end": 5.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into the wilderness unto our father,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.84,
      "end": 8.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he was filled with joy,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.342,
      "end": 10.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my mother, Sariah,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.519,
      "end": 12.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was exceedingly glad,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 12.417,
      "end": 14.832,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for she truly had mourned because of us.",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 15.512,
      "end": 19.041,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For she had supposed that we had perished in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 19.221,
      "end": 22.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and she also had complained against my father,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 22.187,
      "end": 25.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "telling him that he was a visionary man; saying:",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 25.943,
      "end": 30.448,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold thou hast led us forth from the land of our inheritance,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 30.628,
      "end": 32.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my sons are no more,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 32.341,
      "end": 34.57,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we perish in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 35.25,
      "end": 37.526,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 37.706,
      "end": 40.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "had my mother complained against my father.",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 40.987,
      "end": 44.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it had come to pass that my father spake unto her, saying:",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 44.743,
      "end": 47.204,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know that I am a visionary man;",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 47.384,
      "end": 50.588,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for if I had not seen the things of God in a vision",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 50.768,
      "end": 53.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I should not have known the goodness of God,",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 53.595,
      "end": 55.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but had tarried at Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 56.051,
      "end": 58.187,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had perished with my brethren.",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 58.867,
      "end": 61.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I have obtained a land of promise,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 61.601,
      "end": 63.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the which things I do rejoice;",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 64.149,
      "end": 67.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and I know that the Lord will deliver my sons",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 67.766,
      "end": 69.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of the hands of Laban,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 69.804,
      "end": 73.287,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring them down again unto us in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 73.967,
      "end": 76.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 76.423,
      "end": 80.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did my father, Lehi, comfort my mother, Sariah, concerning us,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 80.783,
      "end": 84.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "while we journeyed in the wilderness up to the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 85.096,
      "end": 87.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to obtain the record of the Jews.",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 88.052,
      "end": 91.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when we had returned to the tent of my father,",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 91.576,
      "end": 93.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold their joy was full,",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 93.799,
      "end": 95.796,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my mother was comforted.",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 96.476,
      "end": 98.148,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And she spake, saying:",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 98.328,
      "end": 100.232,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now I know of a surety",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 100.412,
      "end": 104.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord hath commanded my husband to flee into the wilderness;",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 105.143,
      "end": 107.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and I also know of a surety",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 108.156,
      "end": 110.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord hath protected my sons,",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 110.751,
      "end": 113.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and delivered them out of the hands of Laban,",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 113.81,
      "end": 117.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and given them power whereby they could accomplish the thing",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 117.473,
      "end": 119.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the Lord hath commanded them.",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 119.743,
      "end": 122.669,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language did she speak.",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 123.349,
      "end": 126.553,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did rejoice exceedingly,",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 126.733,
      "end": 130.17,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did offer sacrifice and burnt offerings unto the Lord;",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 130.35,
      "end": 132.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they gave thanks unto the God of Israel.",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 133.631,
      "end": 136.65,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had given thanks unto the God of Israel,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 136.83,
      "end": 139.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my father, Lehi, took the records",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 139.239,
      "end": 142.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 143.134,
      "end": 145.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he did search them from the beginning.",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 145.997,
      "end": 149.944,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he beheld that they did contain the five books of Moses,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 150.124,
      "end": 153.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which gave an account of the creation of the world,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 153.323,
      "end": 155.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of Adam and Eve,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 155.407,
      "end": 157.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were our first parents;",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 158.316,
      "end": 161.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also a record of the Jews from the beginning,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 162.118,
      "end": 165.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even down to the commencement of the reign of Zedekiah,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 165.409,
      "end": 166.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "king of Judah;",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 167.436,
      "end": 170.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also the prophecies of the holy prophets,",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 170.356,
      "end": 171.703,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the beginning,",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 171.883,
      "end": 174.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even down to the commencement of the reign of Zedekiah;",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 175.174,
      "end": 177.078,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many prophecies",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 177.258,
      "end": 180.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been spoken by the mouth of Jeremiah.",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 181.142,
      "end": 186.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that my father, Lehi, also found upon the plates of brass",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 186.198,
      "end": 188.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a genealogy of his fathers;",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 188.561,
      "end": 191.858,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore he knew that he was a descendant of Joseph;",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 192.038,
      "end": 194.917,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even that Joseph who was the son of Jacob,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 195.097,
      "end": 196.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who was sold into Egypt,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 197.042,
      "end": 199.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who was preserved by the hand of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 199.916,
      "end": 202.424,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might preserve his father, Jacob,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 202.604,
      "end": 204.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all his household",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 204.409,
      "end": 206.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from perishing with famine.",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 206.854,
      "end": 209.269,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they were also led out of captivity",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 209.449,
      "end": 211.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and out of the land of Egypt,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 211.672,
      "end": 214.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by that same God who had preserved them.",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 214.72,
      "end": 216.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus my father, Lehi,",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 216.804,
      "end": 219.405,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did discover the genealogy of his fathers.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 219.585,
      "end": 222.418,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And Laban also was a descendant of Joseph,",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 222.598,
      "end": 226.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore he and his fathers had kept the records.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 227.133,
      "end": 229.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now when my father saw all these things,",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 229.542,
      "end": 231.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was filled with the Spirit,",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 231.765,
      "end": 234.319,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and began to prophesy concerning his seed\u2014",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 234.999,
      "end": 237.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "That these plates of brass should go forth",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 237.965,
      "end": 240.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto all nations, kindreds, tongues,",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 241.071,
      "end": 243.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and people who were of his seed.",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 244.212,
      "end": 245.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he said",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 245.925,
      "end": 249.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that these plates of brass should never perish;",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 249.216,
      "end": 252.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither should they be dimmed any more by time.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 252.554,
      "end": 255.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he prophesied many things concerning his seed.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 256.392,
      "end": 261.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that thus far I and my father had kept the commandments",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 261.634,
      "end": 264.049,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherewith the Lord had commanded us.",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 264.729,
      "end": 267.051,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we had obtained the records",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 267.231,
      "end": 270.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the Lord had commanded us, and searched them",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 270.801,
      "end": 273.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and found that they were desirable;",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 273.303,
      "end": 275.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even of great worth unto us,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 275.898,
      "end": 280.867,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that we could preserve the commandments of the Lord unto our children.",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 281.547,
      "end": 285.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, it was wisdom in the Lord that we should carry them with us,",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 285.721,
      "end": 289.204,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as we journeyed in the wilderness towards the land of promise.",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 98
    }
  ]
}